<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>Hello there,</p>

    <p>your friend <%= @sender %> wants you to have a look at this voting:<br>
    <a href="<%= url_for controller: "/#{@voting.voting_type}_votings", id: @voting.id.to_s, action: :show %>"><%= @voting.title %></a><br>
    by <%= @voting.user.full_name %>
    </p>

    <p>Have fun with this one and share on.</p>

    <p>The votogenic.io team!</p>
  </body>
</html>
